      "raw_text": "MILES CITY, Mont. May 21.--\nOver $4,000 tons of coal have been\npiled on the prairie near this city\nby the Northern Pacific Railroad\nCo., and much more is to be dump\ned there. These measures are taken\nas a precaution against another\npossible fuel famine. A fence has\nbeen built around the large coal\npile and guards stationed."
    }
